This is a ROMIO ADIO device for Gfarm file system.

INSTALL
---------

This assumes that Gfarm is installed in /usr/local/gfarm_v2.

Downloading mpich2
% wget http://www.mcs.anl.gov/research/projects/mpich2/downloads/tarballs/1.3.2p1/mpich2-1.3.2p1.tar.gz
% tar zxvf mpich2-1.3.2p1.tar.gz

Copying ad_gfarm directory 
% cp -r ad_gfarm mpich2-1.3.2p1/src/mpi/romio/adio/

Applying patch
% patch -p0< mpich2.patch
% cd mpich2-1.3.2p1
% ./maint/updatefiles

Building mpich2
% export CFLAG="-I/usr/local/gfarm_v2/include -lgfarm -L/usr/local/gfarm_v2/lib"
% ./configure --enable-romio --with-file-system=ufs+nfs+gfarm
% make
% make install


